headline: Is United Parcel Service Stock a Buy Despite Tariff Worries?
summary: United Parcel Service operates at the epicenter of the trade war situation since it helps to deliver packages all over the world.  Beginning in 2020, the coronavirus pandemic led investors to drive UPS stock sharply higher.
